{"tid":1355410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港民中聯辦抗議 韓國瑜：我有能力影響中聯辦 不怕再到訪","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:33:28.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"30a236602089818343cff41ceabce5786bbc445d","tid":1355410,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3944745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3944745&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=4a0e920a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3944745</a><br />\n<br />\n主持人詢問香港的一國兩制是否失敗？韓國瑜表示，若沒問題，不會有100多萬港人上街頭，一國兩制原本承諾50年不變，但實施27年就遭受全世界民主國家質疑，北京、香港當局都要思索問題。<br />\n<br />\n主持人再問「中聯辦」也是被抗爭之地，韓國瑜說，未來選擇訪問地點一定要更謹慎，但台灣不能一直怕，「台灣人若對民主自由有堅定信心，到哪都不怕」。韓表示，當時中聯辦官員看著他及高雄訪問團成員大聲聊天、無比信心，「為何不說中聯辦被高雄團影響很大？為何去中聯辦就是賣台，是否有心人士要扣黑帽，我們高雄團隊對中聯辦影響更大」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜強調，「我覺得台灣人不必怕，要把所有『圍牆』拆掉，2020後通往世界都是道路，這就來自我們對民主自由的信心」。"},{"pid":"f18a91da58b97453b9db251922bdedc645945f0c","tid":1355410,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e67d23a4522257a2cf0199edc4f9631b4f3e7e4","tid":1355410,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18a91da58b97453b9db251922bdedc645945f0c","tid":1355410,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1522d3c93d34202b1f8ddfb897eb105c4410ff26","tid":1355410,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"希望佢講多啲<br />\n咁先有得助攻"},{"pid":"e673d80